# Introduction

Many writing systems, notably a handful of East Asian scripts, may be oriented either horizontally or vertically. While
code is generally written left to write and top to bottom, there is no inherent reason this must be the case. In fact,
we will show that vertical writing of code has numerous benefits over traditional horizontal code.

In this paper we propose support for vertical text in C++:

